            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_12\"><span class=\"text_13\">织体概念来自音</span><span class=\"text_14\">乐</span><span class=\"text_13\">&quot;声部</span><span class=\"text_14\">”</span><span class=\"text_13\">就是音乐织体的毛线<br class=\"calibre4\"></span><span class=\"text_14\">&quot;故事的织体”有七个声部<br class=\"calibre4\"></span><span class=\"text_15\">身份</span><span class=\"text_15\">、</span><span class=\"text_15\">欲望</span><span class=\"text_15\">、</span><span class=\"text_15\">动作</span><span class=\"text_15\">、</span><span class=\"text_15\">问题</span><span class=\"text_15\">、</span><span class=\"text_15\">障碍</span><span class=\"text_15\">、</span><span class=\"text_15\">结果</span><span class=\"text_15\">、主题<br class=\"calibre4\"></span><span class=\"text_13\">抓住七根毛</span><span class=\"text_14\">线</span><span class=\"text_13\">织出故事的逻辑与动力</span></p></div>"
