        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000000989": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000000989",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_351\"><span class=\"text_\">幕与关键事件的功能表</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000000990": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000000990",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><table class=\"table_1\">\n\t\t<tbody class=\"calibre11\"><tr class=\"tr_44\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_3\"><p class=\"block_145\"><span class=\"text_\">幕与点</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_4\"><p class=\"block_145\"><span class=\"text_\">内容、功能</span></p></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr class=\"tr_45\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_11\"><p class=\"block_145\"><span class=\"text_\">第一幕</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_9\"><p class=\"block_294\"><span class=\"text_9\">建置</span><span class=\"text_10\">.</span><span class=\"text_9\">基本交待导入主事件</span></p></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr class=\"tr_11\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_3\"><p class=\"block_145\"><span class=\"text_\">激励事件</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_4\"><p class=\"block_145\"><span class=\"text_\">核心问题的发端故事主体的发力点</span></p></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr class=\"tr_45\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_3\"><p class=\"block_352\"><span class=\"text_25\">第二</span><span class=\"text_26\">幕</span><span class=\"text_25\"></span><span class=\"text_25\">上</span><span class=\"text_25\"></span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_4\"><p class=\"block_153\"><span class=\"text_22\">进展</span><span class=\"text_22\"></span><span class=\"text_22\">开始解决核心问题</span></p></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr class=\"tr_11\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_3\"><p class=\"block_145\"><span class=\"text_\">转折事件</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_4\"><p class=\"block_145\"><span class=\"text_\">故事的发展力出现重大的向变或量变</span></p></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr class=\"tr_11\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_3\"><p class=\"block_352\"><span class=\"text_25\">第二</span><span class=\"text_26\">幕</span><span class=\"text_25\"></span><span class=\"text_25\">下</span><span class=\"text_25\"></span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_4\"><p class=\"block_153\"><span class=\"text_22\">转折</span><span class=\"text_22\"></span><span class=\"text_22\">新障碍下解决核心问题</span></p></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr class=\"tr_45\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_3\"><p class=\"block_145\"><span class=\"text_\">危机事件</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_4\"><p class=\"block_145\"><span class=\"text_\">解决核心问题必须跨越的最大障碍</span></p></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr class=\"tr_16\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_6\"><p class=\"block_145\"><span class=\"text_\">第三幕</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_10\"><p class=\"block_153\"><span class=\"text_22\">解决</span><span class=\"text_22\"></span><span class=\"text_22\">最后对决</span><span class=\"text_22\"></span><span class=\"text_22\">交待结果</span></p></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody></table></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000000991": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000000991",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_148\"> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000000992": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000000992",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_64\"><span class=\"text_9\">幕结构基本清晰后接下来就是设计三幕的内容。而作为第三幕主体的 故事</span><span class=\"text_10\">高潮在</span><span class=\"text_9\">“故事织体”环节已经初步成形。以高潮为目标以建置、冲突、 解决为结构逻辑故事三幕的设计方向基本可以确定下来。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000000993": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000000993",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_65\"><span class=\"text_\">三幕方向基本确定后,连接、划分三幕的三个关键事件也就有了设计方向。 设计中重点注意两个问题逻辑性与动力性。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000000994": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000000994",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000000995": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000000995",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"1\" class=\"block_164\"><span class=\"text_\">关键事件是幕与幕的逻辑连接点顺理成章的逻辑性是设计关键事件 的一个重要要求。你不能违反逻辑.不顾观众感受对人物、事件随心所欲 地进行改变或频繁使用巧合来维持你的故事进展。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000000996": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000000996",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000000997": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000000997",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"2\" class=\"block_199\"><span class=\"text_9\">关键事件是故事进展的重要动力合理是关键事件的基本要</span><span class=\"text_10\">求</span><span class=\"text_9\">而对<br class=\"calibre7\">\n</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000000998": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000000998",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000000999": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000000999",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001000": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001000",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"1\" class=\"block_199\">\n<span class=\"text_9\">\n故事发展提供动力是它在故事中更为重要的功能。故事中会有很多事件或 大或小地推动着故事前行。但三个关键事件的推动力更大且具有决定性的 意义。关键事件正是在逻辑性与动力性的双重要求下进行设计的。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001001": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001001",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001002": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001002",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_112\"><span class=\"text_13\">创作程序进行至此三点与三幕岀现了一个基本框架接下来就是向你 的框架中填充内容了。内容从哪里来那</span><span class=\"text_14\">张</span><span class=\"text_25\">“</span><span class=\"text_13\">天大”的灵感分类表应该就挂 在你的工作台前看它把现在用得着的东西一个一个搬下来。有的素材可 能需要变形才能为你所用多看有哪些灵感可以通过改造使用。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001003": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001003",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_112\"><span class=\"text_13\">能用的都用完了怎么办把</span><span class=\"text_25\">“</span><span class=\"text_13\">幕方案表”贴</span><span class=\"text_14\">在</span><span class=\"text_13\">“灵感分类表”的旁边</span><span class=\"text_25\"> </span><span class=\"text_13\">再来一次加了很多限制的天马行空你会有新的收获。直到你的幕方案表中 的三幕与三个关键事件基本清晰才能算是完成了这个步骤。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001004": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001004",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_110\"><span class=\"text_\">笔记以建置、进展、转折、解决为结构逻辑设计三幕内容以逻辑性 和动力性为目标来设计关键事件。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001005": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001005",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001006": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001006",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"9\" class=\"block_353\"><span class=\"text_14\">例 </span><span class=\"text_13\">《翻谱人</span><span class=\"text_34\">》</span><span class=\"text_13\">的关键事件与幕布局</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001007": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001007",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001008": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001008",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_354\"><span class=\"text_\">第一步梳理目前已确定内容</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001009": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001009",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001010": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001010",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"1\" class=\"block_355\"><span class=\"text_9\">故事目</span><span class=\"text_10\">标</span><span class=\"text_9\">一句话</span><span class=\"text_10\">故事</span><span class=\"text_9\"></span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001012": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001012",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_354\"><span class=\"text_\">乐团翻谱人为了证明交响乐的价值面对金钱至上观念带来的思想冲 击和生存挑战去保全一个即将解散的乐团结果失败故事表现了金钱至 上观念下的文化困境。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001013": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001013",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001014": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001014",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"2\" class=\"block_356\"><span class=\"text_\">织体三线和三线的起止点</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"3\" class=\"block_356\"><span class=\"text_\">故事主事件保住乐团</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"4\" class=\"block_356\"><span class=\"text_\">开篇事件主角恶搞排练现场</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"5\" class=\"block_356\"><span class=\"text_\">高潮事件主角率众抗争</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001021",
