            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_71\"><span class=\"text_9\">已</span><span class=\"text_72\">经确定的</span><span class=\"text_9\">“主角恶搞乐团排练”这个开篇事件基本表现了乐团的思想 状态和工作状态乐团弱势的主角因为其过人的商业能力而与乐团关系扭曲。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_71\"><span class=\"text_9\">接下来乐团赖以生存的资本靠山倒塌逼迫乐团必须作出选择解散 还是自救大家都在作自己的利益权衡。有的因为理想有的因为现实最 后大家</span><span class=\"text_72\">一致</span><span class=\"text_9\">或大多</span><span class=\"text_72\">数</span><span class=\"text_9\">决定自救。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_371\"><span class=\"text_9\">一群游走在艺术殿堂的人突然发现都没有自救的技能平时被乐团边缘 化的主角被推上前台。出于对经济</span><span class=\"text_72\">利</span><span class=\"text_9\">益的追求再加上报复性的职业虚荣心 经过一番讨价还价主角半推半就地接手了这个前途未卜的烂摊子。故事主 体就这样讽刺地开始了。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_306\"><span class=\"text_\">第二幕上</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_110\"><span class=\"text_\">幕功能</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_110\"><span class=\"text_\">故事进展开始解决核心问题。第二幕就是要交待保团的初步过程直 到出现一个影响故事向变或量变的事件。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_113\"><span class=\"text_11\">内容大纲</span><span class=\"text_22\"></span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"1\" class=\"block_141\"><span class=\"text_\">乐团自救的初始历程</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"2\" class=\"block_141\"><span class=\"text_\">主角的动机转变</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"3\" class=\"block_141\"><span class=\"text_\">故事的逻辑铺垫和动力积累。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_110\"><span class=\"text_\">内容设计</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_110\"><span class=\"text_\">保团之初理想主义的艺术家们都想寻求一条独立自主的生存之路。作 为有丰富市场经验的主角非常清楚这条路是走不通的但是为了达到不可 告人的个人目的他还是带队走上了救团的不归路。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_110\"><span class=\"text_\">首先尝试寻找时下流行的天使投资失败。负气的乐团决定直面市场的 考验输得更惨。其间出于坚守高雅艺术的尊严乐团果断拒绝了网络直 播平台抛出的橄榄枝。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_111\"><span class=\"text_9\">有意带队跑偏的主角在挫折中慢慢唤醒心底的艺术自尊</span><span class=\"text_72\">心</span><span class=\"text_9\">他的动机也<br class=\"calibre7\">\n</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_111\">\n<span class=\"text_9\">\n从利用乐团牟私利开始向为证明乐团价值转变。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_372\"><span class=\"text_\">万念俱灰的艺术家们无意间发现交响乐居然也有不错的网络流量。乐 团决定抓住网络直播这根救命稻草。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_306\"><span class=\"text_\">第二幕下</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_113\"><span class=\"text_11\">幕功能</span><span class=\"text_22\"></span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_110\"><span class=\"text_\">故事的发展力出现重大的向变或量变直到出现一个解决核心问题的重 要障碍。全新的救团方式将迎来一个更大的麻烦。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_110\"><span class=\"text_\">内容大纲</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"1\" class=\"block_373\"><span class=\"text_\">利用网络平台乐团走一条另类的救团之路</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"2\" class=\"block_259\"><span class=\"text_\">主角开始全情投入越陷越深</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"3\" class=\"block_259\"><span class=\"text_\">故事加速进行动力积累。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_112\"><span class=\"text_13\">内</span><span class=\"text_14\">容设</span><span class=\"text_13\">计</span><span class=\"text_25\"></span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_110\"><span class=\"text_\">为了不受制于人乐团决定独立运营这个自己并不熟悉的新平台。主角 倾其所有注巨资参与这次前途未卜的豪赌。不曾想一个巨大的骗局在等待 这群直播菜鸟。硝烟散去主角血本无归乐团终于走入绝境。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_112\"><span class=\"text_13\">走投无路的乐团不得不委曲求全投身于直播企业的怀抱。变身买方 市场的直播企业为了彰显自己上市的软、硬资本要求乐团</span><span class=\"text_14\">一方面要</span><span class=\"text_25\">“</span><span class=\"text_13\">高 雅其内容”来洗白自己另一</span><span class=\"text_14\">方面还要</span><span class=\"text_25\">“</span><span class=\"text_13\">通俗其形式”来吸引更多的流量。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_374\"><span class=\"text_9\">金主的过分要求招致乐团强烈反感不曾想金主留有后手拉入一个同 样处境艰难的芭蕾</span><span class=\"text_10\">舞</span><span class=\"text_9\">团</span><span class=\"text_10\">与乐团</span><span class=\"text_9\">PK, —个强势的竞争对手来到面前。以为忍辱 就可以偷生的乐团顿时傻眼为生存艺术家们不得不重新调整心态认真准 备与同行一决高下。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_\"><span class=\"text_\">第三幕</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_375\"><span class=\"text_11\">幕功能</span><span class=\"text_22\"></span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_301\"><span class=\"text_\">经历最激烈的冲突迎来核心问题的最终解决。面对生存权与尊严权 主角与乐团作出自己最后的选择。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_376\"><span class=\"text_\">内容大纲</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"1\" class=\"block_377\"><span class=\"text_\">冲突准备过程</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"2\" class=\"block_377\"><span class=\"text_\">爆发点以及爆发方式</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001104": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001104",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001105": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001105",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_378\"><span class=\"text_25\">3</span><span class=\"text_26\">.</span><span class=\"text_13\">事件结果。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001106": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001106",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_379\"><span class=\"text_13\">内容</span><span class=\"text_14\">设</span><span class=\"text_13\">计</span><span class=\"text_25\"></span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001107": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_37\"><span class=\"text_\">一场功能复杂的高雅音乐会是故事的高潮也是第三幕的主体。高潮来 临前还需要一些逻辑和动力方面的准备与积累。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_116\"><span class=\"text_11\">主角救团过程中的价值变化使其与生意合伙人背道而驰</span><span class=\"text_22\"></span><span class=\"text_11\">直至彻底翻脸。 主角社会行骗行迹暴露老年歌舞队上门讨债。更让人意想不到的是网络 结识的红颜知己竟然就是与自己竞争的芭蕾舞团的主演。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_105\"><span class=\"text_13\">音乐会仓促举行经过改造的交响乐团流量表现仍不乐观</span><span class=\"text_14\"></span><span class=\"text_13\">倒是芭蕾舞 团反响不错现场监测统计部门通过大数据和评论反馈发现穿得少是芭蕾 舞团领先的制胜秘密。金主深思良久终于下达了 </span><span class=\"text_25\">“</span><span class=\"text_13\">脱”的最高指令。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_37\"><span class=\"text_\">一直忍辱负重的指挥崩溃了他脱下燕尾服狂笑着离开他苦心经营的 乐团和一辈子热爱的舞台。梦寐以求的指挥棒终于落到主角手上为生存还 是为尊严他必须作出选择。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_37\"><span class=\"text_\">立在舞台正中的主角冲着现场观众和直播机器吼出了他心底积压已久 的愤懑。高雅艺术突然变身为广场歌舞一场不伦不类的高雅音乐会彻底沦 为无厘头的恶搞迎来一场史无前例的网络狂欢。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_380\"><span class=\"text_45\">第</span><span class=\"text_35\">1</span><span class=\"text_78\">0</span><span class=\"text_45\">章</span><span class=\"text_46\">该写故事</span><span class=\"text_45\">梗概了</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_268\"><span class=\"text_29\">1</span><span class=\"text_18\">0</span><span class=\"text_31\">.</span><span class=\"text_18\">1</span><span class=\"text_13\">什么是故事梗概</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_112\"><span class=\"text_13\">故事梗概就是对故事概略性的描述。</span><span class=\"text_25\">“</span><span class=\"text_13\">概略性”是个比较抽象的词前 面讲到的</span><span class=\"text_14\">故事核心表述和</span><span class=\"text_25\">“</span><span class=\"text_13\">一句话故事”都可</span><span class=\"text_14\">以称为</span><span class=\"text_25\">“</span><span class=\"text_13\">概略性”描述只是 概略程度不同而已。这两种描述由于过于概略缺乏很多必要的可读信息 故事的基本面貌不太清晰主要用来作为作者的创作航标。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_112\"><span class=\"text_13\">梗概需要展现故事的基本面貌这</span><span class=\"text_14\">个</span><span class=\"text_25\">“</span><span class=\"text_13\">基本面貌”应该包括故事的主要 内容和大体结构方式。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_113\"><span class=\"text_11\">主要内容是指</span><span class=\"text_22\">&quot;</span><span class=\"text_11\">一句话故事”所体现的内容。故事的主角因为什么样 的欲望针对什么样的事件采取什么样的手段去解决核心问题他遇到了 哪些障碍结果怎样表达了什么思想意义。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_110\"><span class=\"text_\">内容的结构方式是指在幕这个层面上处理、组织故事内容的方法。包 括布局方式、引入方式、积累方式、转折方式、解决方式简单来说就是 指故事的起承转合。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_112\"><span class=\"text_13\">既然是梗概字就不能太多到底多少字也没有一个硬性规定。在把故 事基本面貌说清楚的前提下字越少越好。如果你几十个</span><span class=\"text_14\">字可以说清楚.</span><span class=\"text_13\">当 然可以不过这不太容易。字数最好不</span><span class=\"text_14\">要超过</span><span class=\"text_13\">8</span><span class=\"text_26\">(</span><span class=\"text_25\">0</span><span class=\"text_13\">字它是常规文档一页 纸的容量一满页纸的强制阅读还不至于太难受。如果你要投稿那就按对 方的要求来</span><span class=\"text_25\"></span><span class=\"text_13\">很多都</span><span class=\"text_14\">要求在</span><span class=\"text_13\">3</span><span class=\"text_14\">00</span><span class=\"text_13\">到5</span><span class=\"text_14\">00</span><span class=\"text_13\">字。怎么把字写少也是一个不错的<br class=\"calibre7\">\n</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_112\">\n<span class=\"text_13\">\n练习。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_381\"><span class=\"text_13\">笔记故事梗概就是对故事概略性的描</span><span class=\"text_14\">述</span><span class=\"text_13\">要展示故事的主要内容和大 体结构方式</span><span class=\"text_25\"></span><span class=\"text_13\">字数在3</span><span class=\"text_14\">00</span><span class=\"text_13\">到5</span><span class=\"text_26\">(</span><span class=\"text_13\">0字。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001121": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001121",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_139\"><span class=\"text_26\">10.2</span><span class=\"text_13\">故事梗概有什么朋</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001122": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001122",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_113\"><span class=\"text_11\">故事涉及的创作文本一般是三个梗概、大纲、剧本。三个文本的功能 分别是梗概看故事.大纲看讲法</span><span class=\"text_22\"></span><span class=\"text_11\">剧本看细节。我们常说一个好电影应该是“讲 好一个好故事”梗概呈现的是故事好不好如果故事不好讲得再好也于 事无补。如果通过梗概呈现的故事不错接下来再看大纲看你的故事讲得 好不好。这两关过来才会有研读剧本细节的意义。故事梗概作为故事内容 的初步呈现不但具有推介意义对于修正创作也很重要。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001123": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001123",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_112\"><span class=\"text_13\">通过写故事梗概可以在宏观上修正自己的创作。故事梗概就像一幅画的 白描轮廓构图、布局</span><span class=\"text_14\">、</span><span class=\"text_13\">比例、透视等图画基本要素已经看得比较清楚了</span><span class=\"text_25\"> </span><span class=\"text_13\">你可以对你的作品作进行整体审视。就像画家画画不但要凑在画布前一笔 一笔地画还要经常退后审视一下全局。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001124": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001124",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_111\"><span class=\"text_9\">故事创作是一个细节繁复的活作者很容易陷入某个局部不能自</span><span class=\"text_10\">拔</span><span class=\"text_9\">这 时都需要及时退后一步以观全局。你会发现刚才还自鸣得意的局部根本就是 一堆垃圾或者苦思冥想就在这退一步中豁然开朗了。故事创作中你需要 在特写、近景、全景中不断切换。故事梗概就是你作品的第一次全貌展示 趁一切都还来得及好好看看它。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001125": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001125",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_112\"><span class=\"text_13\">故事梗概是向外推介作品的最简文体。再简略阅读者就看不出故事的 好坏了你给别人一</span><span class=\"text_14\">个需要无限脑补的</span><span class=\"text_13\">“故事说明”还不如直接让他写得了。 如果再具体就是故事大纲了。如果你写一个介于梗概与大纲之间的东西来</span><span class=\"text_25\"> </span><span class=\"text_13\">不但尴尬而且功能意义不大。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001126": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001126",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_382\"><span class=\"text_13\">笔记故事梗概是作品的初次全貌展</span><span class=\"text_14\">示</span><span class=\"text_13\">可以在宏观上修正自己的创作</span><span class=\"text_25\"> </span><span class=\"text_13\">是向外推介作品的最简文体。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001127": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001127",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_383\"><span class=\"text_25\">1</span><span class=\"text_26\">3</span><span class=\"text_13\">故事梗概怎么写</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001128": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001128",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_384\"><span class=\"text_9\">当故事</span><span class=\"text_10\">的创作步骤进行到</span><span class=\"text_9\">“幕布局”环节时故事的三个支柱和八个支 </span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001129": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001129",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_385\"><span class=\"text_9\">点故事要</span><span class=\"text_10\">素</span><span class=\"text_9\">已经比较完整地结构到了一起故事的基本面貌已经出现。 梗概就是把这个基本面貌概略性地描述出来。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001130": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001130",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_122\"><span class=\"text_9\">故事梗概的</span><span class=\"text_10\">写作可以通过故事的</span><span class=\"text_9\">“最简表述”一“简洁表述”一故事梗 概这样一个由简入繁的过程来进行写作练习。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001131": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001131",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001132": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001132",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"1\" class=\"block_386\"><span class=\"text_13\">故事的</span><span class=\"text_14\">最简表述就是</span><span class=\"text_25\">“</span><span class=\"text_13\">一句话故事”仅描述故事的八个要素。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001133": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001133",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001134": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001134",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_88\"><span class=\"text_22\">例1</span><span class=\"text_22\">:</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001135": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001135",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_136\"><span class=\"text_\">乐团翻谱人为了证明交响乐的价值面对金钱至上观念带来的思想冲 击和生存挑战去保全一个即将解散的乐团结果失败故事表现了金钱至 上观念下的文化困境。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001136": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001136",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001137": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001137",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"2\" class=\"block_204\"><span class=\"text_\">故事的简洁表述就是将故事要素略微展开适当展示声部弧光也就 是故事要素在故事中的发展、变化。由于受篇幅限制仅按需展开部分故事 要素且点到为止。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001138": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001138",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001139": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001139",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_136\"><span class=\"text_\">例2</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001140": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001140",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_136\"><span class=\"text_\">资助乐团的企业破产面临解散的交响乐团决定自救。一向不务正业的 乐团翻谱人因为其商业能力被推上救团领导的位置。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001141": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001141",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_122\"><span class=\"text_9\">面对金钱至上观念冲击下的文化市场救团之路步履维艰。为证明交响 乐的价值主角与乐团一直面临尊严与生存的两难选择。天使投资、直面市场、 网络表演自</span><span class=\"text_10\">主谋</span><span class=\"text_9\">生</span><span class=\"text_10\">路</span><span class=\"text_9\">的各</span><span class=\"text_10\">种</span><span class=\"text_9\">尝试与努力均告失败。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001142": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001142",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_136\"><span class=\"text_\">走入绝境的乐团不得不委身于某网络直播企业。面对金主的出尔反尔 和媚俗要求的步步紧逼主角终于忍无可忍率众反击得到一场赢了尊严 输掉生存的悲壮胜利。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001143": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001143",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001144": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001144",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"3\" class=\"block_205\"><span class=\"text_9\">故事</span><span class=\"text_10\">梗概就是在</span><span class=\"text_9\">“简洁表述”的基础上将故事要素进一步展开并 适当表现故事在幕层面的结构方式。最方便的做法是将分幕方案表的内容 连接起来并稍作整理。故事内容就是幕的内容故事的结构方式就是关键事 件主导形成的故事的起承转合。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001145": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001145",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001146": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001146",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_87\"><span class=\"text_25\">例3见「1</span><span class=\"text_26\">0.</span><span class=\"text_25\">例</span><span class=\"text_25\"></span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001147": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001147",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_136\"><span class=\"text_\">笔记故事梗概就是描述幕层面的故事内容和结构方式。可以通过故事的 最简表述一简洁表述一故事梗概的程序进行写作练习。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001148": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001148",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001149": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001149",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"10\" class=\"block_387\"><span class=\"text_11\">例 《翻谱人</span><span class=\"text_2\">》</span><span class=\"text_11\">的故事梗概</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001150": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001150",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001151": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001151",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_388\"><span class=\"text_\">第一步比照分幕方案表</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001152": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001152",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_325\"><span class=\"text_22\">《翻谱人</span><span class=\"text_22\">》</span><span class=\"text_22\">分幕方案表</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001153": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001153",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><table class=\"table_1\">\n\t\t<tbody class=\"calibre11\"><tr class=\"tr_45\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_3\"><p class=\"block_389\"><span class=\"text_\">幕与点</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_4\"><p class=\"block_145\"><span class=\"text_\">内容</span></p></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr class=\"tr_59\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_3\"><p class=\"block_389\"><span class=\"text_\">第一幕</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_5\"><p class=\"block_390\"><span class=\"text_25\">当今</span><span class=\"text_25\"></span><span class=\"text_25\">某沿海二</span><span class=\"text_26\">线城市</span><span class=\"text_26\"></span><span class=\"text_25\">一企业独资的交响乐团</span><span class=\"text_25\"></span><span class=\"text_25\">在金钱至上观念 的冲击下人心涣散。作为乐团翻谱人的主角更是无心本职工</span><span class=\"text_26\">作</span><span class=\"text_25\">打 </span><span class=\"text_25\">着乐团旗号在外坑蒙拐骗倒是风生水起。资助乐团的企业破产</span><span class=\"text_25\">乐 </span><span class=\"text_25\">团面临解散出于理想与现实原因乐团决定自救。</span></p></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr class=\"tr_47\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_3\"><p class=\"block_146\"><span class=\"text_\">激励事件</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_4\"><p class=\"block_391\"><span class=\"text_22\">主角由于出色的商业能力</span><span class=\"text_22\"></span><span class=\"text_22\">被推上救团领导位置。</span></p></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr class=\"tr_59\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_3\"><p class=\"block_280\"><span class=\"text_25\">第二</span><span class=\"text_26\">幕</span><span class=\"text_25\"></span><span class=\"text_25\">上</span><span class=\"text_25\"></span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_4\"><p class=\"block_392\"><span class=\"text_22\">寻找投资</span><span class=\"text_22\"></span><span class=\"text_22\">无人问津</span><span class=\"text_22\"></span><span class=\"text_22\">商人并不看好高雅艺术的商业价值</span><span class=\"text_22\">。</span><span class=\"text_22\">直面市 场</span><span class=\"text_22\"></span><span class=\"text_22\">票房惨败</span><span class=\"text_22\"></span><span class=\"text_22\">交响乐早已被过度娱乐化的文艺市场边缘化。尽管 生存艰难</span><span class=\"text_22\"></span><span class=\"text_22\">乐团与主角仍然不愿媚俗求存。身心俱疲的艺术家们悲 愤地奏响乐团绝唱。</span></p></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr class=\"tr_14\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_11\"><p class=\"block_146\"><span class=\"text_\">转折事件</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_9\"><p class=\"block_28\"><span class=\"text_25\">意外发现流量潜</span><span class=\"text_26\">力</span><span class=\"text_25\"></span><span class=\"text_25\">乐团决定抓住网络直播这一线生机。</span></p></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr class=\"tr_60\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_3\"><p class=\"block_280\"><span class=\"text_25\">第二</span><span class=\"text_76\">幕</span><span class=\"text_25\"></span><span class=\"text_25\">下</span><span class=\"text_25\"></span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_4\"><p class=\"block_390\"><span class=\"text_25\">网络直播遭遇</span><span class=\"text_26\">骗局</span><span class=\"text_25\"></span><span class=\"text_25\">乐团走入绝境主角负债累累</span><span class=\"text_26\">&quot;</span><span class=\"text_25\">乐团不得不委 身于一直不愿合作的直播平台。面对资方得寸进尺的媚俗要</span><span class=\"text_26\">求</span><span class=\"text_25\">乐 </span><span class=\"text_25\">团的艺术尊严节节失守。</span></p></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr class=\"tr_14\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_11\"><p class=\"block_146\"><span class=\"text_\">危机事件</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_9\"><p class=\"block_28\"><span class=\"text_25\">金主突</span><span class=\"text_26\">然变卦</span><span class=\"text_26\"></span><span class=\"text_25\">脚踩两只船</span><span class=\"text_25\"></span><span class=\"text_25\">拉入一舞团</span><span class=\"text_26\">与乐团</span><span class=\"text_25\">PK</span><span class=\"text_25\">。</span></p></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr class=\"tr_61\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_6\"><p class=\"block_291\"><span class=\"text_\">第三幕</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_10\"><p class=\"block_361\"><span class=\"text_25\">强劲的竞争对手对乐团压力巨</span><span class=\"text_26\">大.</span><span class=\"text_25\">投资商得寸进尺的演出要求一步 步逼近艺术家们的心理底线。主角终于忍无可忍</span><span class=\"text_25\"></span><span class=\"text_25\">率众奋起反击 得到一场赢了尊严输掉生存的悲壮胜利。</span></p></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody></table></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001154": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001154",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_203\"> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001155": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001155",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_393\"><span class=\"text_\">第二步梗概写作</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001156": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001156",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_305\"><span class=\"text_\">《翻谱人》故事梗概</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001157": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001157",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_393\"><span class=\"text_\">当今中国某沿海二线城市一支由某企业独资组建的交响乐团。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001158": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001158",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_316\"><span class=\"text_\">主角是交响乐团的助理指挥因为不受首席指挥待见沦为翻谱人。在 金钱至上的社会大环境下乐团人心涣散破罐子破摔的主角利用乐团身份 在外坑蒙拐骗倒是风生水起。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001159": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001159",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_394\"><span class=\"text_\">乐团的东家企业破产乐团面临解散出于对职业梦想的坚持和现实生 活的压力乐团决定自救。主角由于出色的商业能力被推上救团领导位置。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001160": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001160",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_395\"><span class=\"text_\">寻找投资无人问津直面市场票房惨败试水网络遭遇骗局。生存 之路一条条被堵死乐团不得不委身于一直不愿与其合作的某网络直播平台。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001161": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001161",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_219\"><span class=\"text_9\">涉黄丑闻缠身且融资在即的该直播平台为扭转形象并提升流量决定 好好利用交响乐团这个难得的高雅标签。</span><span class=\"text_10\">一场</span><span class=\"text_9\">“高雅其内容、通俗其形式” 的大型网络直播进入筹备。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001162": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001162",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_220\"><span class=\"text_13\">面对资方得寸进尺的媚俗要求乐团的艺术尊严节节失守。可资方仍 然不满足乐团的妥协突然变卦</span><span class=\"text_14\"></span><span class=\"text_13\">拉来一支同样处境艰难的芭蕾舞团与乐团 </span><span class=\"text_25\">P</span><span class=\"text_26\">K,</span><span class=\"text_13\">争夺这一个几近屈辱的生存机会。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001163": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001163",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_128\"><span class=\"text_\">强劲的竞争对手对乐团压力巨大资方得寸进尺的演出要求一步步逼近 艺术家们的心理底线。主角终于忍无可忍率众奋起反击得到一场赢了尊 严输掉生存的悲壮胜利。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001164": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001164",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_399\"><span class=\"text_45\">第</span><span class=\"text_35\">1</span><span class=\"text_78\">1</span><span class=\"text_45\">章</span><span class=\"text_36\">幕的</span><span class=\"text_13\">织体</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001165": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001165",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_63\"><span class=\"text_37\">1</span><span class=\"text_\">织体、逻辑、动力</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001166": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001166",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_400\"><span class=\"text_9\">好故事的标准一向众说纷纭。在“织体”的语境下“符合逻</span><span class=\"text_10\">辑</span><span class=\"text_9\">、进展有力” 是评价故事好坏的重要标准。“故事织体”就是以逻辑性和动力性为目标 在不同结构层次和纵横两个方向上组织故事要素的方式。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001167": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001167",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_401\"><span class=\"text_22\">1</span><span class=\"text_11\">故事的结构层次。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001168": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001168",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_401\"><span class=\"text_11\">一幅书法作品至少有三个结构层级行、字、笔画</span><span class=\"text_22\">“</span><span class=\"text_11\">行”、</span><span class=\"text_22\">“</span><span class=\"text_11\">字”、 </span><span class=\"text_22\">“</span><span class=\"text_11\">笔画”就是三个由大到小的结构单位。字内讲究的是笔画的安排与呼应</span><span class=\"text_22\"> </span><span class=\"text_11\">行内是字与字的结构关系行与行则是作品整体最大的结构趣味。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001169": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001169",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_7\"><span class=\"text_6\"><$image alt=\"Image\" class=\"calibre35\" source=\"$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/images/images/image-23.jpeg\"></$image><$image alt=\"Image\" class=\"calibre36\" source=\"$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/images/images/image-24.jpeg\"></$image></span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001170": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001170",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_402\"><span class=\"text_19\">物收嗖</span><span class=\"text_79\">s&gt;&lt;</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001171": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001171",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_403\"><span class=\"text_50\">夕 </span><span class=\"text_51\">一</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001172": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001172",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_404\"><span class=\"text_80\">-0</span><span class=\"text_46\"> </span><span class=\"text_45\">滋 </span><span class=\"text_81\">4 4</span><span class=\"text_46\">旅</span><span class=\"text_81\">A</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001173": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001173",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_112\"><span class=\"text_13\">故事也至少有三</span><span class=\"text_14\">个结构层级.</span><span class=\"text_13\">它们是幕、序列、场景。</span><span class=\"text_25\">“</span><span class=\"text_13\">幕”、</span><span class=\"text_25\">“</span><span class=\"text_13\">序列”、 </span><span class=\"text_25\">“</span><span class=\"text_13\">场景”就是故事的结构单位。故事的织体就是要搞清楚故事的各个要素 在不同结构层级内的运行方式。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001174": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001174",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_405\"><span class=\"text_6\"><$image alt=\"Image\" class=\"calibre37\" source=\"$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/images/images/image-25.jpeg\"></$image></span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001175": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001175",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_406\"><span class=\"text_\">/\\ /\\ /\\ /\\ /\\ /\\ 场景△△△△△△△△△△△△</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001176": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001176",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_101\"><span class=\"text_25\">2</span><span class=\"text_26\">.</span><span class=\"text_13\">织体的编织方向。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001177": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001177",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_101\"><span class=\"text_13\">不同的结构层级故事要素都会在纵、横两个方向上产生关联。纵向指 的是结构单位内部不同要素之间的作用关系。横向指的是相邻单位间同一 故事要素的作用关系。比如以</span><span class=\"text_25\">“</span><span class=\"text_13\">幕”为结构单位时“问题”这个故事要 素要与幕内</span><span class=\"text_14\">其他故事要素</span><span class=\"text_13\">身份、欲望、动作</span><span class=\"text_14\">…</span><span class=\"text_13\">…纵向相关同时又要与 上、下</span><span class=\"text_14\">幕的</span><span class=\"text_13\">“问题”产生横向关联。这里所谓的纵横是参照的时间轴坐标</span><span class=\"text_25\"> </span><span class=\"text_13\">我们也尽量在对应织体工作表的列表中保持同样方向。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001178": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001178",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_7\"><span class=\"text_6\"></span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001179": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001179",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_407\"><span class=\"text_\">第一幕<span class=\"tab\">      </span>第二幕<span class=\"tab\">      </span>第三幕</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001180": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001180",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_408\"><span class=\"text_9\">身份<span class=\"tab\">      </span></span><span class=\"text_10\">身份<span class=\"tab\">      </span></span><span class=\"text_9\">身份</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001181": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001181",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_409\"><span class=\"text_13\">欲望<span class=\"tab\">      </span></span><span class=\"text_82\">/</span><span class=\"text_14\">欲望<span class=\"tab\">      </span></span><span class=\"text_13\">欲望</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001182": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001182",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_410\"><span class=\"text_9\">动作<span class=\"tab\">      </span></span><span class=\"text_10\">『动作<span class=\"tab\">      </span></span><span class=\"text_9\">动作</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001183": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001183",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_411\"><span class=\"text_25\">问</span><span class=\"text_26\">题</span><span class=\"text_83\">令 </span><span class=\"text_84\">题</span><span class=\"text_26\">&quot;问题题</span><span class=\"text_83\">一——&gt;</span><span class=\"text_26\"> </span><span class=\"text_25\">问题</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001184": {
