            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001233",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_430\"><span class=\"text_13\">笔记故事的</span><span class=\"text_14\">结构单位至少有</span><span class=\"text_25\">“</span><span class=\"text_13\">幕”、“序列”、</span><span class=\"text_25\">“</span><span class=\"text_13\">场景”三个层级 逻辑</span><span class=\"text_14\">性和动力性是织</span><span class=\"text_13\">体的目标</span><span class=\"text_26\"></span><span class=\"text_25\">“</span><span class=\"text_13\">幕的织体”就是以逻辑性和动力性为目标<br class=\"calibre7\">\n</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001234": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001234",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_430\">\n<span class=\"text_13\">\n在幕结构层面和纵横两个方向</span><span class=\"text_14\">上</span><span class=\"text_13\">组织故事要素的方式。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001235": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001235",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_139\"><span class=\"text_38\">11.</span><span class=\"text_30\">2</span><span class=\"text_13\">幕内编织</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001236": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001236",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_71\"><span class=\"text_9\">幕内编织就是把一幕作为一</span><span class=\"text_10\">个</span><span class=\"text_9\">整体的时</span><span class=\"text_10\">间维度</span><span class=\"text_9\">将各个故事要素有</span><span class=\"text_10\">动力</span><span class=\"text_9\">、 符合逻辑地结构在一起属于时间轴上的纵向编织。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001237": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001237",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_70\"><span class=\"text_\">1幕内逻辑编织是指理顺幕内各故事要素之间的因果关系。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001238": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001238",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_70\"><span class=\"text_\">身份、欲望、动作……这些故事要素是有因果关系的。什么身份的人才 会有某种欲望只有在这种欲望的驱动下才会采取某种动作因为什么样的 障碍来对抗人物动作才有了这样的结果这样的结果体现了什么样的故 事意义。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001239": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001239",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_118\"><span class=\"text_11\">这是一个环环相扣的逻辑链条尽管每个环节都会有很多可选方案</span><span class=\"text_22\"></span><span class=\"text_11\">但是, 你选择的方案一定不能游离在逻辑的框架之外这是故事创作必须遵守的规 则或者说是必须要受到的限制。你的想象力就是要被限制在逻辑的框架 之内。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001240": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001240",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_187\"><span class=\"text_9\">这里设计</span><span class=\"text_10\">一幕</span><span class=\"text_9\">“小偷偷钱包”的简单故事将故事要素作如下设定 小</span><span class=\"text_10\">偷</span><span class=\"text_9\">身</span><span class=\"text_10\">份</span><span class=\"text_9\">想求</span><span class=\"text_10\">财</span><span class=\"text_9\">欲望偷钱</span><span class=\"text_10\">包</span><span class=\"text_9\">动</span><span class=\"text_10\">作</span><span class=\"text_9\">他能</span><span class=\"text_10\">得到钱吗</span><span class=\"text_9\">核心问</span><span class=\"text_10\">题</span><span class=\"text_9\"> 尽管乘客</span><span class=\"text_10\">们发现了</span><span class=\"text_9\">障碍但他还是</span><span class=\"text_10\">顺利得手</span><span class=\"text_9\">结果表现当下人们的 自</span><span class=\"text_10\">私与冷漠</span><span class=\"text_9\">意义。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001241": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001241",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><table class=\"table_1\">\n\t\t<tbody class=\"calibre11\"><tr class=\"tr_16\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_3\"><p class=\"block_145\"><span class=\"text_\">声部</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_4\"><p class=\"block_145\"><span class=\"text_\">内容</span></p></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr class=\"tr_45\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_11\"><p class=\"block_145\"><span class=\"text_\">身份</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_9\"><p class=\"block_145\"><span class=\"text_\">小偷</span></p></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr class=\"tr_45\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_11\"><p class=\"block_145\"><span class=\"text_\">欲望</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_9\"><p class=\"block_145\"><span class=\"text_\">求财</span></p></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr class=\"tr_45\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_3\"><p class=\"block_145\"><span class=\"text_\">动作</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_4\"><p class=\"block_145\"><span class=\"text_\">偷钱包</span></p></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr class=\"tr_11\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_3\"><p class=\"block_145\"><span class=\"text_\">问题</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_4\"><p class=\"block_145\"><span class=\"text_\">能得到钱吗</span></p></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr class=\"tr_45\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_3\"><p class=\"block_145\"><span class=\"text_\">障碍</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_4\"><p class=\"block_145\"><span class=\"text_\">乘客发现</span></p></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr class=\"tr_11\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_3\"><p class=\"block_145\"><span class=\"text_\">结果</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_4\"><p class=\"block_145\"><span class=\"text_\">顺利得手</span></p></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr class=\"tr_16\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_6\"><p class=\"block_145\"><span class=\"text_\">意义</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_10\"><p class=\"block_145\"><span class=\"text_\">自私与冷漠</span></p></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody></table></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001242": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001242",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_148\"> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001243": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001243",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_431\"><span class=\"text_13\">这是一个逻辑通顺的结构。但是如果</span><span class=\"text_14\">把其中的</span><span class=\"text_13\">“身份”变成杀手或 者</span><span class=\"text_14\">把</span><span class=\"text_13\">“动作”变成偷纸巾又</span><span class=\"text_14\">或者把</span><span class=\"text_25\">“</span><span class=\"text_13\">结果”变成失手了……</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001244": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000001244",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_432\"><span class=\"text_9\">逻辑编织</span><span class=\"text_10\">的对比方案</span><span class=\"text_9\">下划加粗字</span><span class=\"text_10\">体为变量</span><span class=\"text_9\"></span></p></div>"
        },
