            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_217\"> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000002038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000002038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_118\"><span class=\"text_11\">我们可以用一句话用</span><span class=\"text_22\">“</span><span class=\"text_11\">路标事件”把</span><span class=\"text_22\">“</span><span class=\"text_11\">身份”这个故事要素进行跨序 列连接来检验它在序列连接中的逻辑性。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000002039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000002039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_689\"><span class=\"text_11\">《杀手里昂》的</span><span class=\"text_22\">“</span><span class=\"text_11\">身份”逻辑</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000002040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000002040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_690\"><span class=\"text_9\">里昂这个冷</span><span class=\"text_10\">静</span><span class=\"text_9\">的</span><span class=\"text_10\">旁观者.</span><span class=\"text_9\">因为救下女孩不得已成了女孩的临时监护人。<br class=\"calibre7\">\n</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000002041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000002041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_690\">\n<span class=\"text_9\">\n又因为答应收她为徒使里昂转变成一个爱意萌发的教师。再因为女孩搞清 楚仇家身份后执意要报仇里昂作为一个有真爱的情人努力阻止女孩复 仇……</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000002042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000002042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_95\"><span class=\"text_9\">这</span><span class=\"text_10\">就是</span><span class=\"text_9\">“身份”这个故事要素以路标事件为节点在序列连接、进展 上的合理性。欲望、动作、问题都可以用同样的逻辑推导。障碍与结果依然 属于动力编织重点设计的范畴。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000002043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000002043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_78\"><span class=\"text_\">2.序列间动力编织是指通过调整主角欲望与单位结果之间的鸿沟来 控制序列的稳定性。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000002044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000002044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_95\"><span class=\"text_9\">一个故事要想不断地发展下去就需要不断地创造不稳定因素。故事 的稳定性取决于主角欲望与</span><span class=\"text_10\">结</span><span class=\"text_9\">果间的</span><span class=\"text_10\">鸿沟</span><span class=\"text_9\">鸿沟越大稳定性越差。身份决 定欲望动作和障碍决定结果。来看</span><span class=\"text_10\">一下</span><span class=\"text_9\">《杀手里昂》三、四、五序列的稳 定性。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000002045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000002045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_182\"><span class=\"text_26\"></span><span class=\"text_25\">3</span><span class=\"text_13\">激励序列</span><span class=\"text_25\"></span><span class=\"text_13\">里昂想独善其身却最终救下女孩</span><span class=\"text_25\"></span><span class=\"text_13\">卷入麻烦。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000002046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000002046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_182\"><span class=\"text_25\">0</span><span class=\"text_26\">4</span><span class=\"text_13\">进展序列里昂想尽早摆脱女孩最终却不得不收下这个麻烦的弟子。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000002047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000002047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_182\"><span class=\"text_25\">0</span><span class=\"text_26\">5</span><span class=\"text_13\">转折序列</span><span class=\"text_25\"></span><span class=\"text_13\">里昂想抗拒女孩的爱</span><span class=\"text_25\"></span><span class=\"text_13\">最后却也付出了自己的爱。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000002048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000002048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_639\"><span class=\"text_\">分析结果与欲望的鸿沟每一个序列的动力性就很容易看出来了。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000002049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000002049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_691\"><span class=\"text_25\">《杀手里昂</span><span class=\"text_25\">》</span><span class=\"text_25\">序列</span><span class=\"text_26\">动力</span><span class=\"text_25\">部</span><span class=\"text_26\">分</span><span class=\"text_25\"></span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000002050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000002050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><table class=\"table_1\">\n\t\t<tbody class=\"calibre11\"><tr class=\"tr_14\">\n\t\t\t<td rowspan=\"3\" class=\"td_3\"><p class=\"block_556\"><span class=\"text_\">03</span></p><p class=\"block_211\"><span class=\"text_\">激励</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_9\"><p class=\"block_440\"><span class=\"text_10\">-</span><span class=\"text_9\">身份</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_9\"><p class=\"block_211\"><span class=\"text_\">冷静的旁观者</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_9\"><p class=\"block_211\"><span class=\"text_\">欲望</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_9\"><p class=\"block_19\"><span class=\"text_22\">独善其身</span><span class=\"text_22\"></span><span class=\"text_22\">担心女孩</span></p></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr class=\"tr_48\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_9\"><p class=\"block_211\"><span class=\"text_\">动作</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_9\"><p class=\"block_19\"><span class=\"text_22\">旁观</span><span class=\"text_22\"></span><span class=\"text_22\">谨慎窥视</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td rowspan=\"2\" class=\"td_4\"><p class=\"block_211\"><span class=\"text_\">结果</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td rowspan=\"2\" class=\"td_4\"><p class=\"block_211\"><span class=\"text_\">里昂救了女孩</span></p></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr class=\"tr_48\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_9\"><p class=\"block_211\"><span class=\"text_\">障碍</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_9\"><p class=\"block_19\"><span class=\"text_22\">职业准则</span><span class=\"text_22\"></span><span class=\"text_22\">个人性格</span></p></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr class=\"tr_50\">\n\t\t\t<td rowspan=\"3\" class=\"td_3\"><p class=\"block_439\"><span class=\"text_\">04</span></p><p class=\"block_211\"><span class=\"text_\">进展</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_5\"><p class=\"block_463\"><span class=\"text_\">身份</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_5\"><p class=\"block_211\"><span class=\"text_\">左右为难的临时监护</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_5\"><p class=\"block_463\"><span class=\"text_\">欲望</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_5\"><p class=\"block_463\"><span class=\"text_\">摆脱女孩回归常态</span></p></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr class=\"tr_48\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_4\"><p class=\"block_211\"><span class=\"text_\">动作</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_4\"><p class=\"block_19\"><span class=\"text_22\">劝退女孩</span><span class=\"text_22\"></span><span class=\"text_22\">拒绝教学</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td rowspan=\"2\" class=\"td_4\"><p class=\"block_211\"><span class=\"text_\">结果</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td rowspan=\"2\" class=\"td_4\"><p class=\"block_211\"><span class=\"text_\">里昂收女孩为徒</span></p></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr class=\"tr_44\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_4\"><p class=\"block_211\"><span class=\"text_\">障碍</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_4\"><p class=\"block_211\"><span class=\"text_\">女孩的执着</span></p></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr class=\"tr_48\">\n\t\t\t<td rowspan=\"3\" class=\"td_3\"><p class=\"block_692\"><span class=\"text_\">05 转折</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_9\"><p class=\"block_28\"><span class=\"text_26\">身</span><span class=\"text_25\">份</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_9\"><p class=\"block_211\"><span class=\"text_\">爱意萌发的杀手教师</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_9\"><p class=\"block_211\"><span class=\"text_\">欲望</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_9\"><p class=\"block_211\"><span class=\"text_\">想爱又怕爱</span></p></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr class=\"tr_50\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_9\"><p class=\"block_211\"><span class=\"text_\">动作</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_9\"><p class=\"block_19\"><span class=\"text_22\">开始教学</span><span class=\"text_22\"></span><span class=\"text_22\">感受生活</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td rowspan=\"2\" class=\"td_4\"><p class=\"block_211\"><span class=\"text_\">结果</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td rowspan=\"2\" class=\"td_4\"><p class=\"block_211\"><span class=\"text_\">里昂爱上女孩</span></p></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr class=\"tr_47\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_10\"><p class=\"block_211\"><span class=\"text_\">障碍</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_10\"><p class=\"block_211\"><span class=\"text_\">经纪人劝诫自身理智</span></p></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody></table></div>"
        },
