        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000002065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000002065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_694\"><span class=\"text_\">哪个序列的鸿沟更大哪个稳定性更差可以从上面这个对比表格中清</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000002066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000002066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_695\"><span class=\"text_\">晰解读而且身份、动作和障碍在中间所起的作用也是显而易见的。<br class=\"calibre7\">\n</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000002067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000002067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_695\">\n<span class=\"text_\">\n</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000002068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000002068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_95\"><span class=\"text_9\">控制序列进展的动力强弱原</span><span class=\"text_10\">理与</span><span class=\"text_9\">“幕动力”相同。关键在于设计人物 欲望与结果的差距。差距大动力强差距小动力弱。为了使这种欲望与结果 顺理成章就要在身份、动作、障碍三个要素上作文章。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000002069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000002069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_78\"><span class=\"text_\">笔记序列间逻辑编织是指理顺以路标事件为节点各故事要素在序 列连接上的合理性。序列间动力编织是指通过调整主角欲望与单位结果之 间的鸿沟来控制序列的稳定性。身份决定欲望动作和障碍决定结果。<br class=\"calibre7\">\n</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000002070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000002070",
