            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><table class=\"table_1\">\n\t\t<tbody class=\"calibre11\"><tr class=\"tr_48\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_11\"><p class=\"block_145\"><span class=\"text_\">幕</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_9\"><p class=\"block_211\"><span class=\"text_\">序列</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_9\"><p class=\"block_211\"><span class=\"text_\">场景</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_9\"><p class=\"block_145\"><span class=\"text_\">环节</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_9\"><p class=\"block_145\"><span class=\"text_\">动作</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_9\"><p class=\"block_145\"><span class=\"text_\">对白</span></p></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr class=\"tr_124\">\n\t\t\t<td rowspan=\"4\" class=\"td_3\"><p class=\"block_642\"><span class=\"text_\">第</span></p><p class=\"block_145\"><span class=\"text_\">幕</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td rowspan=\"4\" class=\"td_4\"><p class=\"block_556\"><span class=\"text_\">01</span></p><p class=\"block_211\"><span class=\"text_\">开篇</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td rowspan=\"4\" class=\"td_4\"><p class=\"block_238\"><span class=\"text_\">剧场</span></p><p class=\"block_238\"><span class=\"text_\">日 外景 排练</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_4\"><p class=\"block_145\"><span class=\"text_\">解开内衣</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_5\"><p class=\"block_557\"><span class=\"text_\">主角发现独奏内衣欲 松几次试图重新扎紧 最后反而解开内衣</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_5\"><p class=\"block_28\"> </p></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr class=\"tr_125\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_4\"><p class=\"block_145\"><span class=\"text_\">愤怒的独奏</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_9\"><p class=\"block_238\"><span class=\"text_\">停止演奏 打主角耳光 离开剧场</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_5\"><p class=\"block_28\"> </p></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr class=\"tr_126\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_4\"><p class=\"block_145\"><span class=\"text_\">指挥怒斥</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_5\"><p class=\"block_645\"><span class=\"text_\">指挥怒斥 主角反驳</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_5\"><p class=\"block_480\"><span class=\"text_22\">指挥怒斥主 角不务正业 主角反驳没 </span><span class=\"text_22\">有机会</span><span class=\"text_22\">批 指挥与独奏</span></p></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr class=\"tr_23\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_10\"><p class=\"block_145\"><span class=\"text_\">主角离场</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_7\"><p class=\"block_445\"><span class=\"text_\">指挥气急败坏 主角髙调离场</span></p></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"td_7\"><p class=\"block_28\"> </p></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody></table></div>"
