            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"13\" class=\"block_876\"><span class=\"text_13\">故事的首尾必须是事件。人物、意义动作、价值变化就是构成事件的 三个条件。开篇事件是故事的起点高潮事件是故事的终点故事</span><span class=\"text_14\">的</span><span class=\"text_25\">“</span><span class=\"text_13\">结局</span><span class=\"text_25\">” </span><span class=\"text_13\">是高潮事件的延续。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"14\" class=\"block_877\"><span class=\"text_9\">人物声部、事件声部、主题声部是故事的支柱声</span><span class=\"text_10\">部</span><span class=\"text_9\">由故事三支柱发 展而来。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"15\" class=\"block_878\"><span class=\"text_13\">人物线由</span><span class=\"text_14\">支柱人物</span><span class=\"text_13\">主</span><span class=\"text_14\">角</span><span class=\"text_25\"></span><span class=\"text_13\">发展而来。起止点是故事开篇事件与高潮 事件时主角的身</span><span class=\"text_14\">份</span><span class=\"text_13\">、欲望与动作的状态。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"16\" class=\"block_879\"><span class=\"text_9\">事件声部是指由故事次事件连接而成的线起点是开篇事件终点 是高潮或结局。核心问</span><span class=\"text_10\">题</span><span class=\"text_9\">、主要障碍、结果是事件声部的三要素。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"17\" class=\"block_879\"><span class=\"text_9\">主题声部是由次事件表现出来的意义连接而</span><span class=\"text_10\">成</span><span class=\"text_9\">正价值、负价值是主 题声部的组成要素。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_880\"><span class=\"text_25\">1</span><span class=\"text_14\">&amp;</span><span class=\"text_13\">身份、欲望、动作、核心问题、障碍、结果、主题是组成整个故事 织体的七个声部。故事织体表是故事创作的总谱。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"19\" class=\"block_881\"><span class=\"text_9\">确立故事声部时尽量拉开人物</span><span class=\"text_10\">线</span><span class=\"text_9\">、事件线、主题线的起点与终点的 状态距离使之形成反差。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003121": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003121",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_867\"><span class=\"text_2\">第</span><span class=\"text_99\">9</span><span class=\"text_2\">章<span class=\"tab1\">      </span></span><span class=\"text_11\">关键事件与幕布局</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003122": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003122",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003123": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003123",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"20\" class=\"block_882\"><span class=\"text_9\">线性三幕是一种四乐章的故事结</span><span class=\"text_10\">构</span><span class=\"text_9\">它对应着故事</span><span class=\"text_10\">建置</span><span class=\"text_9\">、进展、转折 和解决这种起承转合的结构功能。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003124": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003124",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003125": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003125",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"21\" class=\"block_876\"><span class=\"text_13\">故事被激励事件、转折事件和危机事件划分成第一幕、第二</span><span class=\"text_14\">幕</span><span class=\"text_13\">上</span><span class=\"text_25\"></span><span class=\"text_13\">、 第二</span><span class=\"text_14\">幕</span><span class=\"text_13\">下、第三幕四个部分。这三个事件引导着故事方向对故事进展 有决定性的意义。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003126": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003126",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003127": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003127",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"22\" class=\"block_875\"><span class=\"text_\">以建置、进展、转折、解决为结构逻辑设计三幕内容以逻辑性和动 力性为目标来设计关键事件。<br class=\"calibre7\">\n</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003128": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003128",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003129": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003129",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003130": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003130",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"1\" class=\"block_875\">\n<span class=\"text_\">\n</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003131": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003131",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003132": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003132",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_883\"><span class=\"text_11\">第</span><span class=\"text_100\">1</span><span class=\"text_11\">章该写故事梗概了</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003133": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003133",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003134": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003134",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"23\" class=\"block_884\"><span class=\"text_13\">故事梗概就是对故事概略性的描述要展示故事的主要内容和大体结 构方式字数</span><span class=\"text_14\">在</span><span class=\"text_25\">3</span><span class=\"text_26\"></span><span class=\"text_13\">0到</span><span class=\"text_25\">5</span><span class=\"text_26\">0</span><span class=\"text_13\">字。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003135": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003135",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003136": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003136",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"24\" class=\"block_885\"><span class=\"text_\">故事梗概是作品的初次全貌展示可以在宏观上修正自己的创作是 向外推介作品的最简文体。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003137": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003137",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003138": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003138",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"25\" class=\"block_886\"><span class=\"text_\">故事梗概就是描述幕层面的故事内容和结构方式。可以通过故事的最 简表述一简洁表述一故事梗概的程序进行写作练习。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003139": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003139",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003140": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003140",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_100\"><span class=\"text_9\">第</span><span class=\"text_43\">1</span><span class=\"text_44\">1</span><span class=\"text_9\">章</span><span class=\"text_10\">幕的</span><span class=\"text_9\">织体</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003141": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003141",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003142": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003142",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"26\" class=\"block_386\"><span class=\"text_13\">故事的</span><span class=\"text_14\">结构单位至少有</span><span class=\"text_25\">“</span><span class=\"text_13\">幕</span><span class=\"text_25\">” </span><span class=\"text_26\">I </span><span class=\"text_25\">“</span><span class=\"text_13\">序列”</span><span class=\"text_14\">、</span><span class=\"text_25\">“</span><span class=\"text_13\">场景”三个层级</span><span class=\"text_14\"></span><span class=\"text_13\">逻辑 性和动力性是织体的目标</span><span class=\"text_25\">“</span><span class=\"text_13\">幕的织体”就是以逻辑性和动力性为目标在 幕结构层面和纵横两个方向上组织故事要素的方式。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003143": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003143",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003144": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003144",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"27\" class=\"block_205\"><span class=\"text_9\">幕内逻辑编织是指理顺幕内各故事要素之间的因果关系。幕内动力 编织针对的是身份的难易、欲望的强弱、动作的正反、障碍的大小。幕内编 织应遵照表达目标、逻辑性、动力性的优先顺序以</span><span class=\"text_10\">及</span><span class=\"text_9\">“已知主导亮点优先” 的原则。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003145": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003145",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003146": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003146",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_887\"><span class=\"text_11\">2&amp;幕间逻辑编织是指理顺以关键事件为节点各故事要素在幕连接上 的合理性。幕间动力编织是指通过调整主角欲望与单位结果之间的鸿沟</span><span class=\"text_22\"> </span><span class=\"text_11\">来控制幕的稳定性。身份决定欲望动作和障碍决定结果。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003147": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003147",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_124\"><span class=\"text_13\">第</span><span class=\"text_39\">1</span><span class=\"text_13\">章</span><span class=\"text_14\">让人物关</span><span class=\"text_13\">系</span><span class=\"text_14\">一</span><span class=\"text_13\">目了然</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003148": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003148",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003149": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003149",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"29\" class=\"block_879\"><span class=\"text_9\">人物是有关系的人物关系对人物行为影响巨大对故事的逻辑</span><span class=\"text_10\">性</span><span class=\"text_9\">、 动力性至关重要人物不能脱离人物关系而孤立存在。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003150": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003150",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003151": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003151",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"30\" class=\"block_885\"><span class=\"text_\">人物关系是故事的逻辑基础和故事发展的重要动力源泉。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003152": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003152",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003153": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003153",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"31\" class=\"block_888\"><span class=\"text_\">人物关系分别以事件和主角为核心可以分为处事人物关系和相互人 物关系。处事人物关系中包含有动力人物和阻力人物相互人物关系包括利 益关系、情感关系和价值关系每种关系下包含有相向人物与相背人物。<br class=\"calibre7\">\n</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003154": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003154",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003155": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003155",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003156": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003156",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"1\" class=\"block_888\">\n<span class=\"text_\">\n</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003157": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003157",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003158": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003158",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"2\" class=\"block_889\"><span class=\"text_\">处事人物关系的设置目标在于围绕故事事件的冲突需求设置出故 事的对抗力为精彩、曲折的故事进展提供动力。相互人物关系的设置目标 在于设置对抗力的人物关系原因为故事对抗力的层次、平衡、变化提供 逻辑支持。人物关系对力影响巨大但绝不是影响力的唯一原因。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003159": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003159",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003160": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003160",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_890\"><span class=\"text_9\">第</span><span class=\"text_43\">1</span><span class=\"text_44\">3</span><span class=\"text_9\">章人物走到幕里来</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003161": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003161",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003162": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003162",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"33\" class=\"block_891\"><span class=\"text_9\">故事创作之初将人物隐没在事件中有利于整体结构设计人物应 该在幕织体完成</span><span class=\"text_10\">后</span><span class=\"text_9\">开始出场。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003163": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003163",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003164": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003164",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"34\" class=\"block_892\"><span class=\"text_13\">围</span><span class=\"text_14\">绕每一幕的</span><span class=\"text_25\">“</span><span class=\"text_13\">事”设置处事人物关系人物就在这两股抗力的需 求中出场。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003165": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003165",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003166": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003166",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"35\" class=\"block_893\"><span class=\"text_\">通过对相互人物关系中利益、情感、价值关系的设置来影响人物的 力向、力度以及力的变化从而影响针对故事事件的动力与阻力。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003167": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003167",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003168": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003168",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"36\" class=\"block_894\"><span class=\"text_9\">人物属性包括身</span><span class=\"text_10\">份</span><span class=\"text_9\">、欲望、动作人物属性决定人物关系人物属性 影响人物的力向和力度以及力变。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003169": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003169",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003170": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003170",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"37\" class=\"block_895\"><span class=\"text_\">不要急着给故事人物取名在创作阶段使用标签式的人物名称对创 作会更有帮助。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003171": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003171",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003172": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003172",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_80\"><span class=\"text_13\">第</span><span class=\"text_39\">1</span><span class=\"text_13\">章</span><span class=\"text_14\">高潮</span><span class=\"text_13\">大纲</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003173": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003173",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_201\"><span class=\"text_\">3&amp;精彩的故事需要高潮高潮影响观众的观影体验决定故事的创作方 向。高潮是故事创作的动力目标和逻辑目标。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003174": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003174",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003175": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003175",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"39\" class=\"block_873\"><span class=\"text_\">高潮大纲是按时间顺序以主动人物为线索以动作回合为单位分 人物、原因、动作、内容、反应等五项内容来记录故事进展并以表格的方 式呈现出来。它让高潮的逻辑与动力一目了然。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003176": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003176",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003177": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003177",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"40\" class=\"block_895\"><span class=\"text_\">率先写作高潮大纲可以为高潮的创作留有最大的自由度率先成型 的高潮还可以成为整个故事创作的精确、清晰的目标。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003178": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003178",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003179": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003179",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_896\"><span class=\"text_13\">第</span><span class=\"text_39\">1</span><span class=\"text_13\">章</span><span class=\"text_14\">故</span><span class=\"text_13\">事路标</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003180": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003180",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003181": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003181",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"41\" class=\"block_897\"><span class=\"text_9\">故事路标是对故事进展有重要意义的事件路标事件的路标点是创作<br class=\"calibre7\">\n</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003182": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003182",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003183": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003183",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003184": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003184",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"41\" class=\"block_897\">\n<span class=\"text_9\">\n者顺利完成创作的</span><span class=\"text_10\">依</span><span class=\"text_9\">靠是吸引观众的故事抓手。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003185": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003185",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003186": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003186",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"42\" class=\"block_882\"><span class=\"text_9\">故事</span><span class=\"text_10\">有</span><span class=\"text_9\">1</span><span class=\"text_10\">0</span><span class=\"text_9\">个路标它们分别是开篇事件、切入事件、激励事件、 进展事件、转折事件、再转事件、危机事件、导入事件、高潮事件、结局。 对故事发展起导航作用。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003187": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003187",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003188": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003188",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"43\" class=\"block_874\"><span class=\"text_\">开篇事件、高潮事件、激励事件、转折事件、危机事件已经在前面步 骤明确。确立故事的路标就是把切入事件、进展事件、再转事件、导入事件 与结局追加、置入故事中。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003189": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003189",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003190": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003190",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"44\" class=\"block_898\"><span class=\"text_9\">故事是有起伏的路标事件是故事波的波峰线性三幕的每次起伏间 隔大</span><span class=\"text_10\">约</span><span class=\"text_9\">1</span><span class=\"text_10\">5</span><span class=\"text_9\">分钟起伏强度大致分为三个档次。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003191": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003191",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003192": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003192",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_74\"><span class=\"text_13\">第</span><span class=\"text_30\">1</span><span class=\"text_3\">6</span><span class=\"text_13\">章</span><span class=\"text_14\">序</span><span class=\"text_13\">列织体</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003193": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003193",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003194": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003194",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"45\" class=\"block_874\"><span class=\"text_\">序列小于幕、大于场景是故事第二层级的结构单位。它包含一个路 标事件以及与该路标事件功能相同的其他事件、场景、环节。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003195": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003195",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003196": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003196",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"46\" class=\"block_882\"><span class=\"text_9\">1</span><span class=\"text_10\">0</span><span class=\"text_9\">个路标事件</span><span class=\"text_10\">把故事分解成</span><span class=\"text_9\">1</span><span class=\"text_10\">0</span><span class=\"text_9\">个序</span><span class=\"text_10\">列.</span><span class=\"text_9\">它们分别是开篇、切入、 激励进展、转折再转、危机导向高潮、高潮、结局。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003197": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003197",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003198": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003198",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"47\" class=\"block_899\"><span class=\"text_22\">-</span><span class=\"text_11\">序列织体”就是以逻辑性和动力性为目标在序列结构层面和纵横 两个方向上组织故事要素的方式。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003199": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003199",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003200": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003200",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_220\"><span class=\"text_13\">4&amp;序列内逻辑编织是指理顺幕内各故事要素之间的因果关系。序列内 动力编织针对的是身份的难易、欲望的强弱、动作的正反、障碍的大小。序 列内编织应遵照表达目标、逻辑性、动力性的优先顺序以</span><span class=\"text_14\">及</span><span class=\"text_13\">“已知主导</span><span class=\"text_25\"> </span><span class=\"text_13\">亮点优先”的原则。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003201": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003201",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003202": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003202",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"49\" class=\"block_889\"><span class=\"text_\">序列间逻辑编织是指理顺以路标事件为节点各故事要素在序列连 接上的合理性。序列间动力编织是指通过调整主角欲望与单位结果之间的 鸿沟来控制序列的稳定性。身份决定欲望动作和障碍决定结果。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003203": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003203",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003204": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003204",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_74\"><span class=\"text_13\">第</span><span class=\"text_30\">1</span><span class=\"text_3\">7</span><span class=\"text_13\">章</span><span class=\"text_14\">序列</span><span class=\"text_13\">人物</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003205": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003205",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003206": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003206",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"50\" class=\"block_877\"><span class=\"text_9\">针对1</span><span class=\"text_10\">0</span><span class=\"text_9\">个序列的核心问题设计具有处事关系的人物新人物因为 新事件而出场。人物设计原</span><span class=\"text_10\">理</span><span class=\"text_9\">、方法与幕人物设计相同。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003207": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003207",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003208": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003208",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"51\" class=\"block_900\"><span class=\"text_\">次要人物设计三原则宁少勿多、高效利用、长线作用。<br class=\"calibre7\">\n</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003209": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003209",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003210": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003210",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003211": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003211",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"1\" class=\"block_900\">\n<span class=\"text_\">\n</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003212": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003212",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003213": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003213",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"2\" class=\"block_873\"><span class=\"text_\">序列层级的相互人物关系与幕人物关系原理相同设置人物间利益、 情感、价值关系为人物在序列事件中力的原因、力的多少、力的变化提供 依据。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003214": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003214",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003215": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003215",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_835\"><span class=\"text_\">53•序列织体编织完成后可以给故事人物取名也可以人物名称与标签 名称夹杂使用。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003216": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003216",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_74\"><span class=\"text_34\">第</span><span class=\"text_18\">1</span><span class=\"text_29\">8</span><span class=\"text_13\">章</span><span class=\"text_14\">故事</span><span class=\"text_13\">大纲</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003217": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003217",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003218": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003218",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"54\" class=\"block_882\"><span class=\"text_9\">故事大纲就是故事的内容要</span><span class=\"text_10\">点</span><span class=\"text_9\">是对故事和故事讲法的描述。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003219": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003219",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003220": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003220",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"55\" class=\"block_874\"><span class=\"text_\">故事大纲是故事交流和推介最重要的文本。作者通过故事大纲可以 整体审视自己的作品对故事的后续创作有指导意义。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003221": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003221",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003222": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003222",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"56\" class=\"block_898\"><span class=\"text_9\">故事大纲要以主角为线索和中心</span><span class=\"text_10\"></span><span class=\"text_9\">展现故事的内容、结构和主题。大 纲的内容选择要有取舍与侧重可以有适当的细节与抒情。大纲行文要简洁 并有画面感。故事大纲前可以单列人物和背景介绍。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003223": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003223",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003224": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003224",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_74\"><span class=\"text_34\">第</span><span class=\"text_18\">1</span><span class=\"text_29\">9</span><span class=\"text_13\">章<span class=\"tab\">      </span>关注</span><span class=\"text_14\">的点</span><span class=\"text_13\">与线</span><span class=\"text_14\">一 </span><span class=\"text_39\">W</span><span class=\"text_13\">作的换位思考</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003225": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003225",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003226": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003226",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"57\" class=\"block_874\"><span class=\"text_\">关注点是指能引起观众重视的故事环节由激发点、关注内容、结束 点组成。关注点分为心理与感官两个层面具有速度、长度、强度三个属性。 关注需要得到满足关注期待可以形成故事动力。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003227": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003227",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003228": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003228",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_201\"><span class=\"text_\">5&amp;关注点的无缝连接便是关注线关注线必须为内容服务关注线要注 意关注点的组合节奏伏笔一分晓作为一种长效关注可以构成关注线但 需要合理运用</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003229": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003229",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003230": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003230",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"59\" class=\"block_889\"><span class=\"text_\">模式是为故事内容服务的心理学是编剧的基础科学持续的吸引力 是故事创作的目标关照观众的关注诉求把握关注线的运行方式适用于 所有模式。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003231": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003231",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003232": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003232",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_139\"><span class=\"text_13\">第</span><span class=\"text_39\">2</span><span class=\"text_29\">0</span><span class=\"text_13\">章</span><span class=\"text_14\">场</span><span class=\"text_13\">景织体</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003233": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003233",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003234": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003234",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"60\" class=\"block_901\"><span class=\"text_\">场景是指统一空间和连续时间内的故事场面小于序列大于环节的 故事构成单位。有价值的动作是故事场景的必备条件。场景与事件是有交集<br class=\"calibre7\">\n</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003235": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003235",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003236": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003236",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003237": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003237",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"60\" class=\"block_901\">\n<span class=\"text_\">\n的两个概念。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003238": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003238",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003239": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003239",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"61\" class=\"block_902\"><span class=\"text_\">场景织体就是以路标事件为核心以实现序列意义为目标以场景 为单位进行故事内容的选择与安排。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003240": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003240",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003241": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003241",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"62\" class=\"block_903\"><span class=\"text_9\">场景的纵向编织主要是以序列为单位进行故事内容的选择。1</span><span class=\"text_10\">•</span><span class=\"text_9\">场景 选择与场景的表达目标。2.环节的选择与关注点。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003242": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003242",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003243": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003243",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"63\" class=\"block_904\"><span class=\"text_\">场景的横向编织是指1.编织场景线调整场景的顺序与节奏。2•编 织场景目标线调整目标相关性与价值起伏的节奏。3.编织关注线检查关 注点的连续性和节奏安排。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003244": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003244",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003245": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003245",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_905\"><span class=\"text_70\">笫</span><span class=\"text_47\">2</span><span class=\"text_29\">1</span><span class=\"text_70\">章环节</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003246": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003246",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003247": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003247",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"64\" class=\"block_902\"><span class=\"text_\">环节是故事的最小结构单位指同等价值的动作或动作交流。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003248": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003248",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003249": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003249",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"65\" class=\"block_906\"><span class=\"text_9\">环节记录就是记录各场景内的每一个环节的环节名</span><span class=\"text_10\">称</span><span class=\"text_9\">、人物动作和人 物对白。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003250": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003250",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003251": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003251",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_907\"><span class=\"text_9\">第</span><span class=\"text_43\">2</span><span class=\"text_44\">2</span><span class=\"text_9\">章</span><span class=\"text_10\">人</span><span class=\"text_9\">物图谱</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003252": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003252",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003253": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003253",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"66\" class=\"block_874\"><span class=\"text_\">人物全家福是指以表格的方式呈现所有故事人物的身份、欲望、动 作在故事开始与结束时的状态按照人物在故事中的重要性排序。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003254": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003254",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003255": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003255",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"67\" class=\"block_882\"><span class=\"text_9\">人物的基</span><span class=\"text_10\">因与经历</span><span class=\"text_9\">简历决定着人物</span><span class=\"text_10\">的性格与能力</span><span class=\"text_9\">特征人物 的性格与</span><span class=\"text_10\">能力决定着人物的欲望与动作</span><span class=\"text_9\">人物要</span><span class=\"text_10\">素</span><span class=\"text_9\">。故事人物的三要素必 须要有人物特征、人物简历作支撑。重点在于逻辑设计难点在于故事中的 呈现方式。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003256": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003256",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003257": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003257",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_908\"><span class=\"text_13\">68</span><span class=\"text_26\">•</span><span class=\"text_14\">人</span><span class=\"text_13\">物图谱就是把故事中的每一个人物按照人物属性、人物特征、人 物简历以表格的方式排列岀来以观察人物达成故事功能的形成过程。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003258": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003258",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_139\"><span class=\"text_13\">第</span><span class=\"text_30\">2</span><span class=\"text_29\">3</span><span class=\"text_13\">章</span><span class=\"text_14\">写</span><span class=\"text_13\">剧本</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003259": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003259",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003260": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003260",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"69\" class=\"block_877\"><span class=\"text_9\">剧本正文应该包括场景信息</span><span class=\"text_10\">标</span><span class=\"text_9\">注、场景描述、对白三个部分。三部分 都需要分行</span><span class=\"text_10\">另起</span><span class=\"text_9\">内容视情况再分行分段。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003261": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003261",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003262": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003262",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"70\" class=\"block_873\"><span class=\"text_\">第一稿素材内容为表达目标服务素材顺序影响表达效果用关键 词和短句作素材的快速连接。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003263": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003263",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003264": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003264",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"71\" class=\"block_903\"><span class=\"text_9\">第二稿剧本的描写分为环境描写与人物描写描写要本着可见、周 到、简洁、准确四条原则。对白的本质是人物的动</span><span class=\"text_10\">作</span><span class=\"text_9\">或者是人物动作的延伸。 对白具有交流、交待、表现、独立审美四个功能。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003265": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003265",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n\t</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003266": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003266",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\"><li value=\"72\" class=\"block_882\"><span class=\"text_9\">第三稿的检查主要针对细</span><span class=\"text_10\">节</span><span class=\"text_9\">兼顾内容与结构。建议搁置一段时间后 自己</span><span class=\"text_10\">检</span><span class=\"text_9\">查还要请别人帮忙检查。不能夜郎自大也别妄自菲薄。</span></li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003267": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003267",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-2cf4b4 twpub-c69c7142dcf77b93-9882b5\"><ol class=\"list_\">\n</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c69c7142dcf77b93/text/000003268": {
            "role": "text",
